Recently,{{When|date=September 2018}} Magic Malta went through a refresh which brought shows such as Carlo's Breakfast Café, Arthur's Drive, etc... News bulletins on Magic Malta are provided by the [[BBC]] at 08:00. 09:00, 12:00, 17:00 and 18:00 daily.
