{{nofootnotes|date=June 2018}} {{Use dmy dates|date=June 2018}} {{Use Indian English|date=June 2018}} {{Orphan|date=March 2015}}
[[File:Building of Ravenshaw Radio.jpg|thumb|Building of Ravenshaw Radio]] [[File:Ravenshaw Radio 2.jpg|thumb|Studio of Ravenshaw Radio]] '''Ravenshaw Radio''' is the community [[radio station]] (CRS) of [[Ravenshaw University]], [[Cuttack]], [[Odisha]], [[India]]. It is the first [[campus]] community radio station in Odisha, and was launched on 14 April 2011, the [[Oriya New Year]]. It was opened by the Vice-Chancellor of Ravenshaw University, Sri [[Devdas Chhotray]].
[[Radio program|Programs]] on Ravenshaw Radio are broadcast through a low-power 50-[[watt (unit)|watt]] [[radio transmitter|transmitter]], and can be heard on 90.4 [[megahertz|MHz]] within an 8 - 10 [[kilometer|km]] [[radius]]. The station caters primarily to the university's students.
==References== *http://www.communityvoices.in/directory/community-media-profile/1357/ *http://www.dnaindia.com/india/report-ravenshaw-radio-goes-air-1531980 *http://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/tp-otherstates/ravenshaw-radio-to-go-on-air-from-april-14/article1684585.ece *http://www.dailypioneer.com/state-editions/bhubaneswar/ravenshaw-radio-to-go-on-air-again-from-today.html *http://ravenshawuniversity.ac.in/website/ravenshaw-radio-%28crs%29.htm *http://www.telegraphindia.com/1131116/jsp/odisha/story_17573526.jsp *http://www.newindianexpress.com/states/odisha/article358275.ece *http://www.odisha.in/news/140/ARTICLE/2153/2011-04-08.html *http://crfc.in/university-radio-to-go-on-air-today/ *http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bhubaneswar/University-radio-to-go-on-air-today/articleshow/25781707.cms *https://web.archive.org/web/20150402122122/http://www.futuregov.asia/articles/orissa-gets-its-first-campus-based-community-radio-station
